1
00:00:05,404 --> 00:00:09,807
That's why you should go … 
It's because you understand you're not qualified

2
00:00:10,560 --> 00:00:12,061
and just tell them about Krishna.

3
00:00:12,499 --> 00:00:15,509
[Volunteers for Hell]

4
00:00:15,699 --> 00:00:20,597
There was a little girl, one of the first little girls, 
like one of these little girls now, and boys.

5
00:00:21,459 --> 00:00:23,223
The cute little children.

6
00:00:24,102 --> 00:00:26,428
So, her name was Saraswati,

7
00:00:26,428 --> 00:00:31,288
the daughter of Malati and Shyama Sundar, 
Prabhupad's original disciples.

8
00:00:31,408 --> 00:00:33,882
And Prabhupada liked her a lot.

9
00:00:33,922 --> 00:00:37,585
You can see some pictures of her, 
like playing with Prabhupad.

10
00:00:40,177 --> 00:00:44,001
He used her as an example once 
about preaching.

11
00:00:44,465 --> 00:00:47,585
He was saying, what does it mean to preach,
“Just like our Saraswati.

12
00:00:47,659 --> 00:00:51,947
She will go up to someone and say, 
to some gentleman and say,

13
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:54,107
“Do you know who is Krishna?

14
00:00:54,329 --> 00:00:57,275
Supreme Personality of Godhead!”

15
00:00:57,275 --> 00:00:58,275
[Laghing]

16
00:00:58,555 --> 00:01:00,156
He said, “That's all.”

17
00:01:00,212 --> 00:01:02,033
[Laughing]

18
00:01:02,177 --> 00:01:07,829
So, we take that risk.

19
00:01:09,047 --> 00:01:10,316
Let's put it this way:

20
00:01:10,316 --> 00:01:13,725
we're ready to go to hell
for this on this point.

21
00:01:17,882 --> 00:01:21,718
It's that important to extend
Kṛṣṇa consciousness to others.

22
00:01:21,718 --> 00:01:24,407
And Gurudev, his famous example,
he'd say,

23
00:01:24,429 --> 00:01:27,747
“If I have five rupees,
I do a five-rupee business.”

24
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:28,995
And that's what it means,

25
00:01:29,002 --> 00:01:31,756
“You've got something, right?

26
00:01:32,535 --> 00:01:35,063
[being] disciple of Guru Maharāj,
Gurudev …”

27
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:39,372
Kaviraj Goswami says,

28
00:01:39,379 --> 00:01:46,022
jagāi mādhāi haite muñi se pāpiṣṭha
purīṣera kīṭa haite muñi se laghiṣṭha
[Cc: Ādi, 5.205]

29
00:01:46,176 --> 00:01:50,251
He's deprecating, 
he's filled with self-deprecation.

30
00:01:50,575 --> 00:01:53,374
“I'm the worst sinner imaginable.

31
00:01:53,636 --> 00:01:59,160
If you hear my name, you'll lose all …

32
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:02,240
whatever piety you've accumulated, 
will be lost.

33
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:05,636
If you vibrate my name, 
you're going to hell.”

34
00:02:06,016 --> 00:02:08,449
He's like … 
that level of self-deprecation.

35
00:02:08,619 --> 00:02:12,183
Then at the same time you think, 
“But what I'm telling you now 
 

36
00:02:12,183 --> 00:02:16,335
about the lotus feet of
Gaura-Nityananda and Radha-Govinda,

37
00:02:16,335 --> 00:02:18,545
there is nothing higher than this.”

38
00:02:18,825 --> 00:02:24,162
So, yes, I'm such a fallen person, 
who am I to weigh in on these things?

39
00:02:24,162 --> 00:02:28,242
But actually it's not me—
some higher power is moving my hand.

40
00:02:28,338 --> 00:02:34,076
So our hope is if some seva
comes to us like that,

41
00:02:37,756 --> 00:02:45,488
and there is no one else, 
[no] superior Vaishnava who can do that,

42
00:02:45,678 --> 00:02:48,700
so it's clear—
something is expected from us.

43
00:02:49,408 --> 00:02:54,887
Then we'll pray to our Guru, 
Gauranga,

44
00:02:54,887 --> 00:02:59,907
Nityananda Prabhu, Radha-Govinda, 
“Please use me,

45
00:02:59,907 --> 00:03:07,815
at least let me not be an obstacle
to the dispensation of your divine mercy.

46
00:03:08,723 --> 00:03:11,847
Use me in some way 
to bring these people

47
00:03:11,847 --> 00:03:15,807
in connection with the lotus feet 
of Guru and Gauranga.”

48
00:03:15,807 --> 00:03:19,068
And as Gurudev said, “You got five rupees? 
You can do a five-rupee business.”

49
00:03:19,213 --> 00:03:23,455
Every disciple has got something 
from Guru.

50
00:03:25,779 --> 00:03:27,117
Share that.

